NK040(thi)045:1: // yum chen gcod kyi brgyud pa'i bskang ba bzhugs so //
NK040(thi)045:3: ma bcos spros bral rgyal ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK040(thi)045:4: gcod kyi phrin las sna tshogs dang //
NK040(thi)045:5: dbang sgrub khyim gcod bsgral mchod dang //
NK040(thi)045:6: me tshag la sogs bcas 'dzom dus //
NK040(thi)045:7: bskang ba'i cho ga 'di nyid gces //
NK040(thi)045:8: bskang ba'i dam rdzas gzhan dang mthun //
NK040(thi)045:9: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa'i rdzas //
NK040(thi)045:11: gdung ba'i dbyangs kyi 'di skad bskang ba'o //
NK040(thi)045:12: gnas 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:13: yum chen shes rab phar phyin rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:14: khyed 'khor dpa' bo mkha' 'gro'i dbus na bzhugs //
NK040(thi)045:15: zhi rgyas dbang drag lha tshogs dang //
NK040(thi)045:16: dpa' bo dpa' mo chos skyong dang //
NK040(thi)045:17: dam can ma srin mkha' 'gro dang //
NK040(thi)045:18: las byed sha za khrag 'thung dang //
NK040(thi)045:19: pho nya srog gcod shan pa'i tshogs //
NK040(thi)045:20: sngon gyi thugs dam dgongs pa bzhin //
NK040(thi)045:21: longs spyod tshogs kyi mchod pa 'di //
NK040(thi)045:22: do nub gnas 'dir thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)045:23: bskang gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK040(thi)045:24: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:25: gnas bya rgod phung po'i ri bo nas //
NK040(thi)045:26: bcom ldan sh+aaka thub rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:27: khyed 'khor dpa' bo mkha' 'gro'i dbus na bzhugs //
NK040(thi)045:29: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:30: gnas seng chen bsnol ba'i khri steng nas //
NK040(thi)045:31: 'jam dpal smra ba'i seng ge rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:33: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:34: gnas g.yu lo bkod pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK040(thi)045:35: rje btsun 'phags ma sgrol mo rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:37: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:39: mkha' 'gro su ka sid+d+hi rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:41: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:42: gnas rgya gar chos kyi pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:43: rje ar+ya de ba rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:45: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:46: gtsang la stod deng ri dgon pa nas //
NK040(thi)045:47: pha dam pa rgya gar sangs rgyas rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:49: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:50: gnas ra sa spang lung gi dgon pa nas //
NK040(thi)045:51: skyob pa sh+aakya ye shes rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:53: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:54: gnas dbus gtsang gnyis kyi sa mtshams nas //
NK040(thi)045:55: skyo ston bsod nams bla ma rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:57: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:58: gnas zangs ri mkhar dmar gyi dgon pa nas //
NK040(thi)045:59: ma cig lab kyi sgrol ma rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:61: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:62: gnas sham po gangs kyi ra ba nas //
NK040(thi)045:63: sras rgyal ba don 'grub rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:65: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:66: dpal chu bo ri yi dgon pa nas //
NK040(thi)045:67: khu sgom chos kyi seng+ge rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:69: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:70: gnas lung smad lcang sar gyi dgon pa nas //
NK040(thi)045:71: pha dol pa zangs thal rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:73: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:74: dpal chu bo ri yi dgon pa nas //
NK040(thi)045:75: rje btsun rgya nag gcer bu rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:77: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:78: gnas rab grong chos kyi pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:79: mkhas grub sangs rgyas rab ston rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:81: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:82: gnas zal mo brag gi dgon pa nas //
NK040(thi)045:83: sangs rgyas dge slong rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:85: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:86: gnas kha rag mun seng gi dgon pa nas //
NK040(thi)045:87: sum pa ras chen rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:89: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:90: gnas ri gang chos kyi dgon pa nas //
NK040(thi)045:91: sangs rgyas gnyen ston rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:93: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:94: 'bang pa bkra shis dgon pa nas //
NK040(thi)045:97: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:98: gnas gar bzhugs chos kyi pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:101: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:102: gnas kahthoga dpal gyi sgrub gnas su //
NK040(thi)045:103: pra dz+ny+aa gu ru rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:105: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:106: gnas dpal 'bar bkra shis dgon pa ru //
NK040(thi)045:107: rdo rje dpal ba rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:109: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:110: gnas dpal 'bar bkra shis dgon pa ru //
NK040(thi)045:111: rdo rje dpal ba rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:113: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:114: snang srid chos sku'i pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:115: nam mkha' rdo rje rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:117: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:118: dga' ldan gnam stong ri khrod nas //
NK040(thi)045:119: shi la ke tu rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:121: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:122: spang skam chos gling ri khrod nas //
NK040(thi)045:125: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:126: don gnyis grub pa'i pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:127: dz+ny+aa na ke tu rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:129: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:130: gnas chos brgyad rang grol pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:131: bya btang kun dga' 'bum pa rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:133: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:134: gnas don gnyis lhun grub pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:135: rje pun+ye la k+sha khyed 'khor ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:136: gnas lhun grub 'od lnga'i pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:137: rje badz+ra rasmi rin khyed 'khor sogs /
NK040(thi)045:138: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:139: gnas stong nyid chos dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:140: rje ga ga badz+ra rin po khyed 'khor ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:141: gnas rang rig rang gsal pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:142: rjeg ga ga ma ti rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:144: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:145: gnas ma bcos lhun grub pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:146: rje ka la badz+ra rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:148: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:149: gnas sku lnga dpal gyi ri khrod nas //
NK040(thi)045:151: ma de'i thugs dam rgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:152: gnas kham gang byang chub gling dgon du //
NK040(thi)045:153: rje chos skyong rgya mtsho rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:155: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:156: gnas kahthoga rdo rje'i gdan steng nas //
NK040(thi)045:157: rje klong gsal snying po rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:159: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:160: gnas gsang sngags rab brtan chos gling nas //
NK040(thi)045:161: rje chos nyid rgya mtsho rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:163: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:164: gnas gdung shug drag po'i dben gnas nas //
NK040(thi)045:165: rje bkra shis mtshan can rin khyed 'khor sogs /
NK040(thi)045:166: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:167: gnas shing sgo gangs kyi rwa ba nas //
NK040(thi)045:168: drung pa nam mkha' rgya mtsho khyed 'khor sogs /
NK040(thi)045:169: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:170: gnas 'khrul pa rang grol pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:171: rje pad+ma chos dbyings khyed 'khor sogs /
NK040(thi)045:172: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:173: gnas snang grags chos sku'i pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:174: rje sangs rgyas grags pa khyed 'khor sogs /
NK040(thi)045:175: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:176: gnas tshogs gnyis lhun grub pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:177: rje nam mkha' chos skyong khyed 'khor sogs /
NK040(thi)045:178: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:179: gnas gang shar rang grol pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:180: rje 'jig med bsam gtan khyed 'khor sogs /
NK040(thi)045:181: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:182: gnas smin grol rgya mtsho'i pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:183: rje kun bzang rnam rgyal rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:185: ma de'i thugs dam rgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:186: gnas snang bzhi mthar phyin pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:187: rje rat+na gu ru rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:189: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:190: gnas bshad sgrub nor bu'i lhun po nas //
NK040(thi)045:191: rje chos kyi rgya mtsho rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:193: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:194: gnas brag gdong bkra shis dge 'phel du //
NK040(thi)045:195: rje rdo rje legs bshad rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:197: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:198: gnas spyi gtsug pad zla'i gdan steng nas //
NK040(thi)045:199: drin chen rtsa ba'i bla ma rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:201: yang na man ngag don brgyud ltar na /
NK040(thi)045:202: nam mkha' rgya mtsho yan sngar ltar la /
NK040(thi)045:203: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:204: gnas mos gus mthar phyin pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:205: rje dri med zhing skyong rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:207: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:208: gnas mkhyen brtse nus mthu'i pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:209: rje tshe dbang mchog grub rin khyed 'khor sogs /
NK040(thi)045:210: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:211: gnas stong nyid bde chen pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)045:212: rje nges don dbang po rin khyed 'khor sogs /
NK040(thi)045:213: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:214: gnas rtog 'khrul rang grol yang dben nas //
NK040(thi)045:215: rje 'gyur med bstan 'dzin rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:217: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:218: gnas byang chub seng+ge'i nags khrod nas //
NK040(thi)045:219: rje chos kyi blo gros khyed 'khor sogs /
NK040(thi)045:220: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:221: gnas phyogs med dpal gyi gnyen khrod nas //
NK040(thi)045:222: rje kun bzang 'gyur med rin khyed 'khor sogs /
NK040(thi)045:223: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:224: gnas bshad sgrub nor bu'i lhun po nas //
NK040(thi)045:225: rje chos kyi rgya mtsho rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:227: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:228: gnas brag gdong bkra shis dge 'phel nas //
NK040(thi)045:229: rje rdo rje legs bshad rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:231: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:232: gnas spyi gtsug pad zla'i gdan steng nas //
NK040(thi)045:233: drin chen rtsa ba'i bla ma rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:235: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:236: gnas gnyan sa ri khrod kyi dgon pa nas //
NK040(thi)045:237: grub thob gcod yul brgyud pa rin po che //
NK040(thi)045:239: ma de'i thugs dam brgyud 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)045:240: dam can ma sring rgya mtsho'i tshogs //
NK040(thi)045:241: khyed rnams thugs dam bskang ba'i dam rdzas ni //
NK040(thi)045:243: ma sring mkha' 'gro'i thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)045:245: ma sring mkha' gser g.yu mu tig brgyan cha 'di //
NK040(thi)045:246: ma sring mkha' nyi zla mi ro'i rgyal mtshan 'di //
NK040(thi)045:247: ma sring mkha' ban+d+ha 'bar ba'i gsol sder 'di //
NK040(thi)045:248: ma sring mkha' 'bru sna dgu'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK040(thi)045:249: ma sring gnam rgyan sprul pa'i mchod pa 'di //
NK040(thi)045:250: ma sring mkha' sha sna lnga'i ri bo 'di //
NK040(thi)045:251: ma sring mkha' bam chen rnying pa rul pam 'di //
NK040(thi)045:252: ma sring mkha' zhag dang khrag gi rgya mtsho 'di //
NK040(thi)045:253: ma sring mkha' 'gro'i b+han+d+ha stag sprod rnga sgra 'di //
NK040(thi)045:254: ma sring rkang chen gsang ba'i gling bu 'di //
NK040(thi)045:255: ma sring tshil chen gsang ba'i dud sprin 'di //
NK040(thi)045:256: ma sring mkha' sil spos kyi dud pa 'di //
NK040(thi)045:257: ma dang mkha' 'gro'i rus pa'i phreng ba rgyan drug 'di //
NK040(thi)045:258: ma sring mkha' 'gro'i thugs sna tshogs dar gyi cod pan 'di //
NK040(thi)045:259: ma sring mkha' 'gro'i thugs dam gdung ba'i sgra dbyangs sna tshogs 'di //
NK040(thi)045:260: ma sring mkha' ldem 'dzum 'khril sbyor gar 'khyams 'dis //
NK040(thi)045:261: ma sring rus brgyan gsang ba'i na bza' 'di //
NK040(thi)045:262: ma sring mkha' 'gro'i lcang lo mdzes pa'i rgyan cha 'di //
NK040(thi)045:263: ma sring mkha' phyag mtshan kha t+w+aam gri gug dang //
NK040(thi)045:264: ma sring 'dod yon gtor ma'i mchod rdzas 'di //
NK040(thi)045:265: ma sring mkha' khyed kyi thugs dam bdag gi bskang //
NK040(thi)045:266: rnal 'byor bdag cag yon mchod kyi //
NK040(thi)045:267: 'khor rnams bsrung la rkyen rnams bzlog /
NK040(thi)045:268: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsol //
NK040(thi)045:269: lha 'de mi gsum dbang du bsdus //
NK040(thi)045:270: bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
